{"tid":633124,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[8年前既今日青雞面終於比人收皮］人獨自難敵寒霜 仿似躺於雪地上","createTime":"2018-04-18T04:32:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T16:40:40.000Z","uid":33006,"like":7,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"3260e8c2ea7320f18c5266983ad8b3edb5afb05e","tid":633124,"uid":33006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T04:32:11.000Z","msg":"8年前既今日tvb神劇 鐵馬尋橋播出大結局<br />\n<br />\n全世界人係個類似酒樓既地方聲討青雞面呢幕真係大快人心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n睇住佢恰顧家恰左廿鳩幾集 終於要收皮 仲要眾叛親離咁 真係咪話唔過癮<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/l0yptepXJIM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fl0yptepXJIM&d=3BDfBKm6Na1HOiHBfCacPZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=260a3ee4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/l0yptepXJIM</a><br />\n<br />\n呢套神劇兩條時間線既鋪排 <br />\n加上劇情有幾緊湊幾正唔洗再講<br />\n<br />\n不如再講下比較鍾意咩角色啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我講d冷門d既 <br />\n<br />\n首投梁湛 不解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/18/122906_2a21b2ad540ed8dec4a45f98b39431a8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F18%2F122906_2a21b2ad540ed8dec4a45f98b39431a8.png&h=911ded12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外 周大姐之後明白左青雞面有幾仆街 <br />\n大大聲話本左盤身家都同青雞面死過呢個轉變都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/18/123203_916344e28e24600b11995639449efbbd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F18%2F123203_916344e28e24600b11995639449efbbd.png&h=b6f2d1ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d43f79ccc1eee154579940b492ae7cf077948b37","tid":633124,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T06:07:23.000Z","msg":"放下啦，榮老弟"},{"pid":"3d96e7c78401d8581fc07f7bac85036b7b80d415","tid":633124,"uid":277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T07:40:32.000Z","msg":"七省拳王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e2e740d18652198c79055560d9b8fa37fd3aa90","tid":633124,"uid":53736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T07:45:18.000Z","msg":"一腳踢死顧汝章"},{"pid":"08f8ba87966c552ae53952bf3732807060a0f1ef","tid":633124,"uid":33006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e2e740d18652198c79055560d9b8fa37fd3aa90","tid":633124,"uid":53736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T07:45:18.000Z","msg":"一腳踢死顧汝章"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T08:25:17.000Z","msg":"第二腳呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a67d3888ac9f9f64a8e2959588bd7d95fd225f6","tid":633124,"uid":159293,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T08:27:10.000Z","msg":"先唔討論鐵司尋橋<br />\n可唔可以唔好用「不解釋」呢類用語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔該"},{"pid":"56a8703706fc26f939a71bab7d66635c4aee41d8","tid":633124,"uid":159293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a67d3888ac9f9f64a8e2959588bd7d95fd225f6","tid":633124,"uid":159293,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T08:27:10.000Z","msg":"先唔討論鐵司尋橋<br />\n可唔可以唔好用「不解釋」呢類用語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔該"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T08:27:29.000Z","msg":"馬＊"},{"pid":"3a1095ce03247900dd81dadf9c2d8011478147c4","tid":633124,"uid":818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T08:29:01.000Z","msg":"當年真係晚晚追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <im